::FZ::

FZ raises an eyebrow, not sure what was going on. He had sent out the 
clone of KitKat, and it had just returned, and obviously didn't even 
remember being here.

"I think your memory chips are damaged," he says, walking into the 
Iron Fist and motioning for KitKat2 to follow. "You need Squizzy to 
have a look at them."

He recieves Diamond's messge, activating his comm-link. "Excellent," 
he says into the device, "Can you take them to lab 3? Lady Hawk is 
waiting for them there."
